dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents road centerlines for Dane County, Wisconsin at year-end 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Dane_Roads_2017.gdb. [This layer is a detailed line coverage of the Dane County roadway network containing attributes such as street name and address ranges, ZIP codes, speed limits and routing.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[A comprehensive street centerline and address range database to support Dane County geocoding, routing, and a cartographic product for official mapping.]
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Dane County Land Information Office [Dane LIO maintains this dataset with assitance from the Dane County Surveyor, Dane County Planning & Development - Land Records Division, Dane County 911 Communication and local municipalities.]
